(183, 1, 1, 'there_will_be_blood_xlg.jpg', 'none', 'Paul Thomas Anderson', 'none', '1', 'none', 'Daniel Day-Lewis\nPaul Dano', 'xhtml', '<p>When Daniel Plainview gets a mysterious tip-off that there&#39;s a little town out West where an ocean of oil is oozing out of the ground, he heads there with his son, H.W., to take their chances in dust-worn Little Boston. In this hardscrabble town, where the main excitement centers around the HOLY ROLLER church of charismatic preacher Eli Sunday, Plainview and H.W. make their lucky strike. But even as the well raises all of their fortunes, nothing will remain the same as conflicts escalate and every human value--love, hope, community, belief, ambition, and even the bond between father and son--is imperiled by corruption, deception, and the flow of oil.</p>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, 'Paul Thomas Anderson, based on "Oil!" by Upton Sinclair', 'none', '', NULL, 'American History\nCapitalism\nEvangelical Christianity\nIndependent film', 'xhtml', 'JoAnne Sellar, Paul Thomas Anderson, Daniel Lupi', 'none', '', 'none', '$25 million', 'none', '$76.2 million', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '91%', 'none', '92%', 'none', 'http://www.miramax.com/movie/there-will-be-blood/', 'none', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FeSLPELpMeM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none'),
(185, 1, 1, 'b70-2079.jpeg', 'none', 'Stanley Kubrick', 'none', '1', 'none', 'Peter Sellers\nGeorge C. Scott\nSterling Hayden\nKeenan Wynn\nSlim Pickens', 'xhtml', '<p>Through a series of military and political accidents, a psychotic general - U.S. Air Force Commander Jack D. Ripper (Hayden) - triggers an ingenious, irrevocable scheme to attack Russia&#39;s strategic targets with nuclear bombs. The U.S. President (Sellers) and Dr. Strangelove (Sellers), a wheelchair-bound nuclear scientist who has bizarre ideas about man&#39;s future, work with the Soviet premier in a desperate effort to save the world.</p>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, 'Stanley Kubrick, Peter George, Terry Southern', 'none', '', NULL, 'Black comedy\nCold War\nPolitical satire\nSexual satire\nWar', 'xhtml', 'Stanley Kubrick', 'none', 'Columbia Pictures', 'none', '$1.8 million', 'none', '$9,440,272', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '100%', 'none', '96%', 'none', '', 'none', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IutX5AGEYZc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none'),
(189, 1, 1, 'Vertigomovie_restoration.jpg', 'none', 'Alfred Hitchcock', 'none', '1', 'none', 'James Stewart\nKim Novak\nBarbara Bel Geddes\nTom Helmore\nHenry Jones', 'xhtml', '<p>Hitchcock&#39;s romantic story of obsession, manipulation and fear. A detective is forced to retire after his fear of heights causes the death of a fellow officer and the girl he was hired to follow. He sees a double of the girl, causing him to transform her image onto the dead girl&#39;s body. This leads into a cycle of madness and lies.</p>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, 'Alec Coppel, Samuel Taylor', 'none', '', NULL, 'Alfred Hitchcock\nAuteur\nJames Stewart\nKim Novak\nobsession\nSan Francisco', 'xhtml', 'Alfred Hitchcock', 'none', 'Paramount Pictures', 'none', '$2,479,000', 'none', '$14,000,000', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z5jvQwwHQNY" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none'),
(190, 1, 1, 'citizen-kane-old-poster.jpg', 'none', 'Orson Welles', 'none', '1', 'none', 'Orson Welles\nJoseph Cotten\nDorothy Comingore\nEverett Sloane\nRay Collins\nGeorge Coulouris\nAgnes Moorehead\nPaul Stewart\nRuth Warrick\nErskine Sanford\nWilliam Alland', 'xhtml', '<p>When a reporter is assigned to decipher newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane&#39;s (Orson Welles) dying words, his investigation gradually reveals the fascinating portrait of a complex man who&nbsp;rose from obscurity to staggering heights. Though Kane&#39;s friend and colleague Jedediah Leland (Joseph Cotten), and his mistress, Susan Alexander (Dorothy Comingore), shed fragments of light on Kane&#39;s life, the reporter fears he may never penetrate the mystery of the elusive man&#39;s final word, "Rosebud."</p>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, 'Herman J. Mankiewicz, Orson Welles', 'none', '', NULL, 'Classic Hollywood\nOrson Welles\nRKO', 'xhtml', 'Orson Welles', 'none', 'RKO Radio Pictures', 'none', '$686,033', 'none', '$1,585,634', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zyv19bg0scg" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none'),
